          <p className="text-zinc-300 leading-relaxed">Use PostCraft&apos;s <a href="/story-planner" className="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300">Story Planner</a> to map out your weekly Story content with narrative arcs, engagement stickers, and strategic CTAs that drive DM conversations and conversions.</p>
